        "educational_intro": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>The Shift Toward Intentional Fashion</h3><p>For years, fashion in India was defined by the 'it-bag'—heavy, logo-laden accessories that often felt more like an anchor than a companion. But as we move into 2026, a new philosophy is emerging. It's called <em>Intentional Fashion</em>.</p><p>It's the idea that what we carry should be a reflection of our values as much as our style. This is why the <strong>Nova Everyday Clutch</strong> has become a quiet sensation. It doesn't scream for attention, yet it commands it through the sheer complexity of its hand-woven texture.</p>",
            "text_size": 18
          }
        },
        "brand_weaving": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>\"True luxury is the knowledge that your piece was touched by human hands, not just a conveyor belt.\"</h3><p>When Blissway first began collaborating with artisan weavers, the goal was simple: to create a silhouette that felt as at home in a South Delhi brunch as it did at a Mumbai art gallery. The result is a bag that breathes. The crochet-inspired weave allows for a natural flexibility that rigid luxury leathers simply can't offer.</p>",
            "text_size": 18
          }
        },
        "wear_test_report": {
          "type": "two_column",
          "settings": {
            "image_position": "right",
            "title": "The 180-Day Wear Test: Why it doesn't 'age' like other bags.",
            "text": "<p>Most high-street bags begin to peel or lose their shape within 90 days. We tracked a Nova Clutch through a full Indian season—from the scorching 45°C Delhi summer to the 90% humidity of a Mumbai monsoon.</p><p><strong>The result?</strong> The UV-treated fibers didn't fade a single shade, and the weave remained as tight as day one. Unlike leather which cracks in the heat, this silhouette actually softens and moves better with you over time. It is a piece built for longevity, not just a season.</p>",
            "background_color": "#F3F0EB"
          }
        },
        "capacity_guide": {
          "type": "two_column",
          "settings": {
            "image_position": "right",
            "title": "A Study in Practical Form",
            "text": "<h3>Designed for the 'Pro Max' Reality</h3><p>Most luxury clutches are useless because they don't fit modern life. We tested 14 prototypes just to ensure an iPhone 15 Pro Max fits *with* its case, alongside your keys, a power bank, and a curated selection of cosmetics.</p><h3>What It Isn't</h3><p>This is a piece of wearable art, not a utility hauler. It will not fit a laptop. It is designed to keep you light, intentional, and unfettered.</p>",
            "button_text": "EXPLORE THE SILHOUETTE",
            "button_color": "#1A1A1A"
          }
        },
        "comparison_table": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>The Benchmark of Quality</h3><ul><li><strong>Feature</strong><strong>Blissway Nova Clutch</strong><strong>Mass Market Luxury</strong></li><li><span>Construction</span><span>Hand-Woven Artisan Weave</span><span>Machine Stitched</span></li><li><span>Durability</span><span>Sustainable Tropical-Proof Fiber</span><span>Fragile Synthetic / Cracking Leather</span></li><li><span>Versatility</span><span>Clutch to Crossbody (Gold Chain)</span><span>Single-purpose Silhouettes</span></li><li><span>Value</span><span>Artisan-Direct Pricing</span><span>High Brand Markups (300%+)</span></li></ul>",
            "text_size": 16
          }
        },
        "social_status_angle": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Prepare to be asked: \"Where did you get that?\"</h3><p>There is a specific phenomenon our community calls the <strong>'Stranger Stop.'</strong> Because the Nova Clutch lacks a loud, flashy logo, it creates an air of mystery that people are drawn to.</p><p>We’ve had customers report being stopped in airport lounges and wedding receptions by women carrying bags 10x the price, all asking about the texture. It is the ultimate 'If you know, you know' piece—a conversation starter that signals a refined, creative taste rather than just a budget.</p>",
            "text_size": 18
          }
        },
