          "type": "bullet_points",
          "settings": {
            "point_1": "<strong>The Heritage Look:</strong> Pair Champagne Gold with a silk Kanjeevaram.",
            "point_2": "<strong>The Modern Minimalist:</strong> Match Ivory with monochromatic linens.",
            "point_3": "<strong>The After-Hours:</strong> Use Midnight Black as a clutch for evening soirées.",
