        "trust_and_genuinity": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>The Mark of Genuinity & Coastal Durability</h3><p>In an age of digital filters, the tactile reality of the Blissway weave is its own certification. Because each bag is hand-woven, no two pieces are perfectly identical. These slight variations are the fingerprints of the artisan.</p><p>Our gold hardware is <strong>Triple-Plated</strong> and salt-spray tested. It is specifically engineered not to turn black or green, even in the most humid coastal climates of Mumbai or Chennai. We source only high-grade, sustainable fibers that offer the luster of silk with the ruggedness required for the Indian climate.</p>",
            "text_size": 17
          }
        },
        "concierge_payment": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>A Seamless Acquisition & COD Verification</h3><p>We believe the experience of acquiring a Blissway piece should be as refined as the bag itself. We trust our artisans so much that we want you to see the work before you pay.</p><p>Use our <strong>Verified COD</strong> service to check the bag's weight and weave at your doorstep before finalizing your investment. For digital transactions, our gateways are secured with 256-bit encryption, ensuring your privacy is as guarded as your style.</p>",
            "text_size": 17
          }
        },
