            "text": "<h3>Concierge Inquiries</h3><p><strong>What if the gold polish fades?</strong><br>It won't. We use a premium anti-tarnish coating. If any fading occurs within 1 year, our 'Heirloom Warranty' ensures we will replace the bag for you.</p><p><strong>Will it fit my large phone with a case?</strong><br>Absolutely. We tested the Nova with the iPhone 15 Pro Max and Samsung S24 Ultra inside standard cases. It clicks shut perfectly.</p><p><strong>Is the COD really hassle-free?</strong><br>Yes. You pay the delivery partner only after the package is in your hands. If you are not satisfied, you can refuse it on the spot.</p><p><strong>What if I want to return it later?</strong><br>Blissway offers a 30-day 'Heirloom Guarantee'. Just WhatsApp our concierge, and we’ll arrange a free reverse-pickup from your home.</p>",
